imdb.plot outline: Bahar is a young humble girl who is adopted by a poor, but envious woman named Nuran and Ilias construction worker who falls under the bad influence of Nuran. When they are forced to give back the adopted Bahar to a rich family whom she is born in, they decide to give their legit not so naive daughter Efsun. The life of Bahar begins to change.
